&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Location: Cork City, , Ireland - Hybrid 2 days per week in Office.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for an SDR to join our Cork team, focused on the UK and Ireland market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be responsible for generating outbound pipeline — identifying the right prospects, starting meaningful conversations, and booking qualified meetings for our Account Executive team. You&#39;ll work a defined territory, get to know your market deeply, and build the foundations of a long-term career in B2B sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an individual contributor role, ideal for someone with around a year of SDR experience who is looking for a structured environment to grow, hit targets, and develop toward an Account Executive position.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Be Doing: &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Outbound prospecting and pipeline generation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Research and identify target accounts across the UK and Ireland, run personalised outbound sequences across email, phone, and LinkedIn, and book quality discovery calls for the AE team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Market focus&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Develop a genuine understanding of your territory — the key verticals, typical buyer personas, and what makes them tick in the UK and Irish market context.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tool-led selling&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Use our sales tech stack (Salesforce, Outreach, LinkedIn Sales Navigator, ZoomInfo) to manage your pipeline, track activity, and keep your data clean and accurate.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI-powered productivity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We actively encourage SDRs to incorporate AI tools into their daily workflow — from prospecting research to message personalisation. If you&#39;ve started building these habits, we want to hear about it.&lt;/p&gt;
